# React Patterns

Read `docs/CODING_STANDARDS.md` and `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md`.

## Components

- Functional only; `type Props = { ... }` then `export function Name({ ... }: Props)`
- One component per file; `key={entity.id}` on lists

## Feature Module Files

```
<Feature>Page.tsx      — client orchestrator (filters, dialog state)
<Feature>Table.tsx    — presentation + delete actions
<Feature>Form.tsx     — create/edit, calls Server Actions
<Feature>CreateDialog.tsx / <Feature>EditDialog.tsx — Sheet wrapper
index.ts              — barrel exports
```

## Client Page Pattern

```tsx
"use client";
const [open, setOpen] = useState(false);
const filtered = useMemo(() => items.filter(...), [items, filter]);
// Table + CreateDialog(open) + EditDialog(selected)
```

## Forms

- `useTransition` for pending; `router.refresh()` after mutation
- `toast.success/error` from sonner
- `space-y-5` form layout; `onSuccess={() => setOpen(false)}`

## Tables

- Empty state: `rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 py-16 text-center text-zinc-500`
- Wrapper: `overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950`
- Delete: `confirm()` → Server Action → toast → refresh

## Dialogs

- Use `Sheet` from `@/components/ui/sheet`, not raw dialog
- `sm:max-w-lg`, `SheetTitle`, form in `mt-6` div

## Hooks

- Clean up Supabase channels in `useEffect` return
- Shared hooks go in `hooks/` (when created)
